➜广东诗人辉哥：鹏城小雪
http://www.sohu.com/a/433976943_100115135	29537
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201124/3379b7822b6f496e8cff90b03d2bbc94.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鹏城小雪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/辉哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小雪如常无入冬，南风惯见绿葱茏；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">骄阳百里疑初夏，骗得山花满树红。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201124/b8cffa7a812849418fa168d9e30d24f3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>▲<strong>【作者简介】：</strong>围炉诗情辉哥，来自广东梅县客家，自小在客家农村长大，对客家文化情有独钟。喜爱古诗词，涂鸦作品多用于自耍。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201124/6ea3170e2aa44b858e35d260f3ae78af.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
